rComments: First year teacher and it showed. Lectures were pretty much useless and consisted of him reading over lecture slides. Made a difficult class even more difficult.

He was a good professor, especially for this first time teaching. Comes to class late the second half of the semester and kept us late, which was a little annoying. Otherwise, he did a great job and I feel like I understood the material better than students who took the course the year or two prior.
